                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/ManuNH98" target="_blank" class="grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-900/70 transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-yellow focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-yellow" aria-label="Perfil de Twitter de Manuel Navarro">
